Module kivakit.resource
Package com.telenav.kivakit.resource

Interface ResourceFolder

All Superinterfaces:
UriIdentified
All Known Implementing Classes:
Folder, Package
public interface ResourceFolder extends UriIdentified
A resource container is an abstraction that provides access to hierarchical resources, independent of implementation. Folder is a ResourceFolder, but is also a resource container.
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
